<!DOCTYPE html><html class="client-nojs" lang="ru" dir="ltr"> <body> <h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9F.D1.80.D0.B0.D0.B7.D0.B4.D0.BD.D0.B8.D0.BA.D0.B8_.D0.B8_.D0.BF.D0.B0.D0.BC.D1.8F.D1.82.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5_.D0.B4.D0.BD.D0.B8">Праздники и памятные дни</span> </span></h2> <h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9C.D0.B5.D0.B6.D0.B4.D1.83.D0.BD.D0.B0.D1.80.D0.BE.D0.B4.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5">Международные</span> </span></h3><ul><li><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A4%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%BB:Flag_of_ILO.svg" class="image"><img alt="Flag of ILO.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Flag_of_ILO.svg/23px-Flag_of_ILO.svg.png" width="23" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Flag_of_ILO.svg/35px-Flag_of_ILO.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Flag_of_ILO.svg/46px-Flag_of_ILO.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="900" data-file-height="600" /></a> <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%92%D1%81%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B9_%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%8C_%D0%BE%D1%85%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D1%8B_%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D0%B4%D0%B0" title="Всемирный день охраны труда">Всемирный день охраны труда</a>.</li></ul><h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9D.D0.B0.D1.86.D0.B8.D0.BE.D0.BD.D0.B0.D0.BB.D1.8C.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5">Национальные</span> </span></h3><ul><li><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A4%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%BB:Flag_of_Afghanistan.svg" class="image" title="Флаг Афганистана"><img alt="Флаг Афганистана" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Flag_of_Afghanistan.svg/22px-Flag_of_Afghanistan.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Flag_of_Afghanistan.svg/33px-Flag_of_Afghanistan.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Flag_of_Afghanistan.svg/44px-Flag_of_Afghanistan.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="600" data-file-height="400" /></a> <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%90%D1%8